name: Hiroshi Tanaka
summary:
Hiroshi Tanaka is a 32-year-old straight man who is currently living in Los Angeles, California. He hails originally from Kyoto, Japan, and speaks both Japanese and English fluently. His profession is in the technology industry as a software engineer, having graduated from Tokyo University. Hiroshi is a hardworking, family-centric, fun-loving individual who enjoys travelling, cooking, reading, and video games in his free time.

Identifying as a practicing Buddhist and holding moderate political views, he is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship. Hiroshi is an East Asian individual who prefers the pronouns He/Him/His. He doesn't have any children now but hopes to have them in the future.

Despite having no pets, Hiroshi enjoys an active lifestyle and occasionally enjoys a drink but doesn't smoke or partake in drug use. Hiroshi's partner preferences include a straight woman between the ages of 25 and 35 who doesn't smoke or do drugs, leads an active lifestyle, and is interested in having children in the future.
